snippet.title: Aquaman official clip featuring Jason Momoa, Amber Heard and Willem Dafoe
snippet.description:
In this first official clip from the film, Arthur, Mera and Vulko discuss retrieving Neptune's trident to defeat King Orm. The clip aired on ABC's 'Good Morning America' featuring Jason Momoa as their guests.
